scaledmarkets.dabl.helper

Class Helper

  • java.lang.Object
    • scaledmarkets.dabl.helper.Helper

  • public class Helper
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience methods for traversing the final AST and Annotations that are produced by the DABL compiler.

      • convertArtifactSetToPatternSets

        public PatternSets convertArtifactSetToPatternSets(java.lang.String namespaceName,
                                                   java.lang.String taskName,
                                                   POartifactSet artifactSet,
                                                   PatternSets.Map patternSetsMap,
                                                   RemoteRepo.Map remoteRepoMap)
                                            throws java.lang.Exception
        Convert the specified artifact set into an equivalent PatternSets. Construct a Repo object as needed (a PatternSets applies to a repo). If the Repo already exists in the RemoteRepo map, use that - and so the artifact set for that repo is merged into the existing artifact set for that repo. Similarly, if a PatternSets already exists for the repo/project combination that is specified by the artifact set, then use that PatternSets - and thus merge the pattern into that PatternSets object.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
